# Next Gold Application
# Static assets directory for CSS, JS, images, and other public files

# This directory will contain:
# - Compiled CSS and JavaScript files (via Vite)
# - Images and media files
# - Downloadable documents
# - Temporary upload files

# Directory structure will be created automatically by Laravel and Vite:
# /build/ - Compiled assets from Vite
# /storage/ - Symbolic link to storage/app/public
# /css/ - Additional CSS files
# /js/ - Additional JavaScript files
# /images/ - Application images
# /uploads/ - Temporary upload files
